Flash2Unity
A way to using Flash 2D animations and frame controls in Unity.
Support drawing in Flash IDE and export pngs to Unity.
Automatic packing sprite to SpriteAltas.
Support nextFrame,prevFrame,gotoAndStop,gotoAndPlay,stop.
Support move,scale,rotation,alpha for Sprite and MovieClip.
Simple source code,easy to modify.
Support Unity class reflect by class name.


Requires Unity 2017 or above, which supprot SpriteAltas.
Sample fla file and empty fla file in folder.

 
Using Flash/Animate IDE to edit 2D animations.
Fully tested on OSx.
